history.content: Just as the title says. I just want to get an idea as to how much CS162 is of help in EE192. I've already done the core CS classes (61A, B, C and 70), and I'm planning to do CS 188 and CS 189 before doing EE 192. (Of course, I'm also planning to do EE 120, EE C106A and B). I want to understand what core concepts / ideas (if at all) CS 162 provides for the mechatronics class 192. Thanks!
history.subject: CS162 required/helpful for EE192?
